								<p><span class="text-uppercase">Designer:</span> Leonardo Fioravanti for Pininfarina (Styling) and Nicola Materazzi (Engineer) Limited</p>
								<p><span class="text-uppercase">Series:</span> 1 of 273</p>
								<p><span class="text-uppercase">Parent Company:</span> Ferrari S.p.A/FIAT</p>
